text: Kim Roussakoff (born January 4, 1996) is a Swedish ice hockey defenceman. He is currently playing with Frölunda HC of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Roussakoff made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Frölunda HC during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Frölunda HC players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen
